===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|ang|yfel}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*ubilaz}} (compare {{cog|stq|eeuwel}}, {{cog|nl|euvel}}, {{cog|nds|Övel}}, {{cog|de|übel}}), from {{inh|en|ine-pro|*h₂upélos}}, diminutive of {{m|ine-pro|*h₂wep-|*h₂wep-, *h₂wap-|treat badly}} (compare {{cog|hit|tr=huwappi|gloss=to mistreat, harass}}, {{m|hit|tr=huwappa|gloss=evil, badness}}), or alternatively from {{m|ine-pro|*upélos||evil|lit=going over or beyond (acceptable limits)}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*upo}}, {{m|ine-pro|*up}}, {{m|ine-pro|*eup||down, up, over}}.

